WEBVTT

00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:03.581
[This talk contains mature content]

00:00:04.913 --> 00:00:09.365
Moritz Riesewieck: On March 23, 2013,

00:00:09.389 --> 00:00:13.446
users worldwide
discovered in their news feed

00:00:13.470 --> 00:00:18.533
a video of a young girl
being raped by an older man.

00:00:19.478 --> 00:00:23.334
Before this video
was removed from Facebook,

00:00:23.358 --> 00:00:27.974
it was already shared 16,000 times,

00:00:27.998 --> 00:00:31.640
and it was even liked 4,000 times.